v1.0, 07/10/2012 -- Initial release.
v1.1, 11/10/2012 -- Added WaitingSht1x, dew point calculation and using v4 constants.
v1.2, 31/12/2012 -- Added the possibility to define the GPIO mode (GPIO_BOARD or GPIO_BCM) in the constructor.
v1.3, 28/01/2016 -- Fixing the fact that from version 0.5.11 GPIO.cleanaup() unsets the current pin mode. Cleaning up only the pins that have been set.
